  "body": {
    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p /><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"dc91e5fe-2a75-43d6-8900-a34f69bd06a5\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>For Rendering to Disk only. Checkpoints and recovery are ignored for interactive rendering.</p></div></div><h3 id=\"CheckpointsandRecovery-Recovery\">Recovery</h3><p>Recovery allows us to resume/recover from the previously paused or incomplete stopped render.  To turn it on, check <strong>Recover Render</strong><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\"> in RenderMan RIS ROP's </span><strong>Advanced </strong><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">Tab. </span></p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645601/recover.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433143415&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=850&amp;height=174\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544645601/recover.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433143415&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"174\" data-width=\"850\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544645628\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"recover.PNG\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544645601\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"deb55507-6ec4-4529-b230-113d9ddc43c2\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645601/recover.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433143415&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=850&amp;height=174 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645601/recover.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433143415&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=850&amp;height=174 1x\"></span><p /><h3 id=\"CheckpointsandRecovery-Checkpoints\">Checkpoints</h3><p>Render recovery is often used with checkpointing.  To turn it on, check <strong>Recover Render</strong><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\"> in RenderMan RIS ROP's </span><strong>Advanced</strong> &gt; <strong>Render </strong>Tab<span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">.</span></p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645601/checkpoint.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433143605&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=841&amp;height=390\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544645601/checkpoint.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433143605&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"390\" data-width=\"841\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544645631\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"checkpoint.PNG\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544645601\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"de55c9a6-32a5-446c-99ed-21c58146eb13\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645601/checkpoint.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433143605&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=841&amp;height=390 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544645601/checkpoint.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433143605&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=841&amp;height=390 1x\"></span><p /><ul><li><p>Interval - the time between checkpoint saves</p></li><li><p>Exit At - Exit the render at this time and render no more</p></li><li><p>As Final - Even if the render completes, save the data necessary to pick up the render. This will result in a larger file</p></li><li><p>Keep Files - Name and preserve all the past checkpoints instead of only the more recent one</p></li><li><p>Command - Command for the RIB file location (if one is generated)</p></li></ul><p /><p><strong>Incremental Renders</strong></p><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-warning conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"9a981336-bda8-443a-bff1-900564561122\" data-macro-name=\"warning\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-error confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>Incremental renders are not recoverable without checkpointing enabled. With incremental on and checkpoints off, the buckets are not written out until the end of the render. See table below:</p></div></div><p /><p /><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table data-table-width=\"1800\" data-layout=\"default\" data-local-id=\"5b512d38-b1a4-410e-a9d1-29a0f59cd0f7\" class=\"confluenceTable\"><tbody><tr><th class=\"confluenceTh\"><p><strong>incremental</strong></p></th><th class=\"confluenceTh\"><p><strong>checkpoints</strong></p></th><th class=\"confluenceTh\"><p><strong>recoverable</strong></p></th></tr><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>On</p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>Disabled</p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>No</p></td></tr><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>On</p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>Enabled</p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>Yes</p></td></tr><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>Off</p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>Disabled</p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>Yes</p></td></tr><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>Off</p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>Enabled</p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>Yes</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><em>Recoverable Render Settings</em></p><p /><p /><p><strong>Recovery and 'keepfiles'</strong></p><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-warning conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"347ed2ad-c399-44c7-9b70-56ee7b7d7316\" data-macro-name=\"warning\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-error confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>Do not enable the keepfiles option for checkpointing if you want to use the recover capability.</p><p><sup>Option &quot;checkpoint&quot; &quot;uniform int keepfiles&quot; [0]</sup></p></div></div><p /><p>The keepfiles option causes prman to save a sequence of checkpoints for debugging purposes giving each checkpoint image a unique file name tagged with increment and elapsed render time. However, when attempting to recover a file, prman won't scan your directory for checkpointed files or try to choose one. It will only look for the file by the original render output name.</p><p><em> </em><br/></p>"
    }
  },
